        Obtain the level tuple for a given level; override data available

        ilvl - level number for which to obtain the data

        startAtRestart - startAt value for restarts
        restartLim - limiter index for the restart of this level number
        startAtFirst - effective (overridden) startAt value for the initial run (no restart)
        resetsNumbering - if then this override resets the running number of this level
